parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: A unique, case-sensitive identifier that is provided to ensure the idempotency of the request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the domain where you want to post a data lineage event.

parameters.name: event
parameters.description: The data lineage event that you want to post. Only open-lineage run event are supported as events.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the lineage event.
